# Process Protection Rule

## CRITICAL - Do NOT Touch Existing Processes

This project (Navigator) runs alongside other applications on this server. **NEVER**:

- Stop, kill, or shutdown ANY existing process
- Restart nginx, redis, mongod, docker, PM2, or any node processes
- Modify ports used by: dedsec-training, CyberSentinal, serve (3001), PM2 (5000)
- Change Redis (6379), MongoDB (27017), or system services

## Safe Operations

- Only start/stop processes that belong to **this** Navigator application
- Use unique ports for Navigator (e.g., 5001) that don't conflict
- Navigator uses: Redis (existing), PostgreSQL (Navigator DB only), its own app process
